This is an example domain model mapped on HibernateOGM and using Hibernate Search to provide the query functionalities needed for the Twitter demo,
planned as Keynote presentation of JBoss World 2011 in Boston.

Shows how to configure Hibernate OGM, Infinispan, the JBoss Transaction Manager, and how queries could be implemented to load the required statistics;
please get in touch for any explanation needed, on the mailing list, forums or irc:

https://forum.hibernate.org/
http://hibernate.org/community/mailinglists
http://hibernate.org/community/irc

-- Sanne
